      "raw_text": "William Roberts, a robust lum-\nberjack, was dismissed by Judge\nMann yesterday afternoon after\nhearing for completely in Tuesday\nnights rioting. The case of r\nWiley, alleged to have boarded a\nWashington Water Power Co. car\nto threaten A. M. Macho, an EN-\nployment agent, after the latter\nhad escaped the mob, was con\ntinued till next Wednesday, that\nmore evidence can be secured."
